{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}

'''Wilhelm Hasse''' was a German-born Mexican brewer and founder of [[Dos Equis]].

In 1884 Wilhelm Hasse emigrated from his homeland and established the Moctezuma brewery in [[Veracruz]], [[Mexico]].  In 1897, Hasse blended his brewing heritage with the spirit of Mexican tradition to create [[Dos Equis]].

